thought:
**Determining the New Administrative Unit for "Phường Bình Minh, Thị xã Nghi Sơn, Tỉnh Thanh Hóa"**

Okay, so I've been asked to find the new administrative unit for "Phường Bình Minh, Thị xã Nghi Sơn, Tỉnh Thanh Hóa."  My first step, as always, is to methodically check the relevant resolutions and lists. I'll need to confirm if there are any province-level changes first, but since Thanh Hóa isn't listed for mergers in 60-NQ/TW, it remains "Tỉnh Thanh Hóa."

Now, I'll focus on the sub-province level. Specifically, I'm looking for "Phường Bình Minh" in the "Other resolutions" concerning Thanh Hóa. After a quick search, I find Resolution 1686/NQ-UBTVQH15, which deals with administrative rearrangement in Thanh Hóa. Bingo! Line 141 explicitly states that "phường Hải Hòa, **Bình Minh**, Hải Thanh và xã Hải Nhân" are merged to form "phường Tĩnh Gia."  Given the context of Thị xã Nghi Sơn (implied because all the affected wards/communes are in Nghi Sơn), I'm confident this is the relevant "Phường Bình Minh."

Next, to be thorough, I check the "New wards" list for "Phường Tĩnh Gia" in "Tỉnh Thanh Hóa."  The entry `{"ward_code":"16561","ward_name":"Phường Tĩnh Gia","province_name":"Tỉnh Thanh Hóa"}` confirms the match perfectly.

Therefore, my conclusion is that the new ward is "Phường Tĩnh Gia" with code "16561" in "Tỉnh Thanh Hóa." I'd assign a high confidence level because the resolution is very clear about the merger.

Just to be absolutely certain, I re-examined Resolution 1686 to see if there was any ambiguity. All the other entries within the resolution that address re-arrangements are also tied to Thị xã Nghi Sơn. So, it is reasonable to be assured that the "Phường Bình Minh" referenced is indeed the one in Thị xã Nghi Sơn. It looks like it is all aligned. I will now format the response in the required array of objects.

citation.header: 1686/NQ-UBTVQH15: Sắp xếp các đơn vị hành chính cấp xã của tỉnh Thanh Hóa
citation.line: 141. Sắp xếp toàn bộ diện tích tự nhiên, quy mô dân số của các phường Hải Hòa, Bình Minh, Hải Thanh và xã Hải Nhân thành phường mới có tên gọi là phường Tĩnh Gia.
